    QueueProxy -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext<br/>No auth (pod-internal)"| ModelPod
    ModelPod --- AgentSidecar

    %% Storage Flows
    StorageInit -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>IAM credentials"| S3
    StorageInit -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>GCP SA"| GCS

